{
	"nodes":[
		{"id":"users","type":"text","text":"### 👤 users\n**Core Identity Table**\n\n- `id`: text **(PK)** - Clerk user ID\n- `role`: text - patient | doctor | admin\n- `isAnonymous`: boolean\n- `isAvailable`: boolean *(doctors)*\n- `autoAcceptReservations`: boolean\n- `displayName`: text\n- `bio`: text\n- `languages`: text[]\n- `defaultSessionDuration`: int *(45)*\n- `createdAt` / `updatedAt`: timestamp","x":0,"y":-450,"width":460,"height":410},
		{"id":"patient-private-data","type":"text","text":"### 🛡️ patient_private_data\n**1-to-1 with patient**\n\n- `id`: serial **(PK)**\n- `userId`: text → **users.id (FK)**\n- `fullName`, `phone`, `dateOfBirth`\n- `street`, `city`, `country`\n- `emergencyName`, `emergencyPhone`, `emergencyRelationship`\n- `medicalHistory`: text *(encrypted)*\n- context: text\n- `medications`, `allergies`\n- `createdAt` / `updatedAt`","x":-700,"y":20,"width":400,"height":410},
		{"id":"consent-records","type":"text","text":"### ✅ consent_records\n**Crisis consent audit**\n\n- `id`: serial **(PK)**\n- `userId`: text *(hashed)* → **users.id**\n- `consentType`: text\n- `consentGiven`: boolean\n- `timestamp`: timestamp\n- `appVersion`: text\n- `ipCountryCode`: text","x":-700,"y":500,"width":400,"height":340},
		{"id":"user-subscriptions","type":"text","text":"### 📅 user_subscriptions\n**1-to-many per user**\n\n- `id`: serial **(PK)**\n- `userId`: text → **users.id (FK)**\n- `planId`: int → **subscription_plans.id (FK)**\n- `clerkSubscriptionId`: text\n- `status`: active | trialing | past_due | canceled\n- `currentPeriodStart` / `End`\n- `sessionsUsedThisPeriod`: int\n- `createdAt` / `updatedAt`","x":-1150,"y":420,"width":360,"height":380},
		{"id":"appointments","type":"text","text":"### 📋 appointments\n**Central session record**\n\n- `id`: serial **(PK)**\n- `patientId`: text → **users.id (FK)**\n- `doctorId`: text → **users.id (FK)**\n- `scheduledTime`: timestamp\n- `durationMinutes`: int\n- `status`: pending | confirmed | in_progress | completed | cancelled | no_show\n- `patientIsAnonymous`: boolean\n- `patientRevealedIdentity`: boolean\n- `roomKey`, `roomUrl`, `liveKitToken`\n- `startedAt`, `endedAt`\n- `notes`: text *(encrypted)*","x":0,"y":50,"width":460,"height":450},
		{"id":"schedule-blocks","type":"text","text":"### 🚫 schedule_blocks\n**Blocked time windows**\n\n- `id`: serial **(PK)**\n- `doctorId`: text → **users.id (FK)**\n- `startTime` / `endTime`: timestamp\n- `reason`: text\n- `createdAt`","x":1150,"y":420,"width":360,"height":260},
		{"id":"crisis-events","type":"text","text":"### 🚨 crisis_events\n**Permanent audit log (non-PII)**\n\n- `id`: serial **(PK)**\n- `sessionId`: text *(hashed)*\n- `eventTimestamp`: timestamp\n- `triageResult`: CRISIS | FALSE_ALARM\n- `triageReason`: text\n- `escalationPath`: therapist_confirmed | therapist_cancelled | auto\n- `authorityContacted`: boolean\n- `timeToEscalationMs`: int\n- `consentRecordId`: text","x":700,"y":500,"width":420,"height":420},
		{"id":"authority-notify","type":"text","text":"### 🚔 Authority Notification\n**Emergency services handoff**\n\n**Received:**\n- GPS coordinates *(lat/long)*\n- City + district *(human-readable)*\n- Session reference ID\n- Event timestamp\n- Therapist name + callback\n\n**Patient identity:**\nLocation + session ref only\n\n**Redundancy:**\nIf unanswered → retry 8s → fallback SMS","x":1700,"y":700,"width":400,"height":430},
		{"id":"fk-legend","type":"text","text":"**Legend**\n- Solid arrow = Foreign Key relationship\n- `→` points to referenced table (PK)\n- Patient & Doctor both reference `users.id`\n- Crisis tables use hashed IDs for privacy","x":-1150,"y":-560,"width":340,"height":270},
		{"id":"title","type":"text","text":"# 🌳 ZenDoc Database Architecture\n## PostgreSQL Schema + Crisis Safety Pipeline\n*Obsidian canvas for data model visualization*","x":-240,"y":-1040,"width":700,"height":140},
		{"id":"db-header","type":"text","text":"## 🗄️ Core Database Schema (Drizzle ORM)","x":-240,"y":-720,"width":400,"height":80},
		{"id":"session-usage","type":"text","text":"### ⏱️ session_usage\n**Billing consumption log**\n\n- `id`: serial **(PK)**\n- `userId`: text → **users.id (FK)**\n- `subscriptionId`: int → **user_subscriptions.id (FK)**\n- `appointmentId`: int → **appointments.id (FK)**\n- `sessionDate`: date\n- `durationMinutes`: int\n- `createdAt`","x":0,"y":880,"width":420,"height":340},
		{"id":"subscription-plans","type":"text","text":"### 💳 subscription_plans\n**Plan definitions**\n\n- `id`: serial **(PK)**\n- `clerkPlanId`: text *(unique)*\n- `planName`: text\n- `sessionsPerMonth`: int\n- `sessionsPerWeek`: int\n- `sessionDurationMinutes`: int\n- `priceMonthly`: int *(cents)*\n- `features`: text[]\n- `createdAt`","x":-1150,"y":-140,"width":360,"height":380},
		{"id":"doctor-qualifications","type":"text","text":"### 🎓 doctor_qualifications\n**1-to-many per doctor**\n\n- `id`: serial **(PK)**\n- `doctorId`: text → **users.id (FK)**\n- `type`: degree | certification | license | award\n- `title`: text\n- `institution`: text\n- `yearObtained`: int\n- `expiryDate`: date\n- `documentUrl`: text\n- `verificationStatus`: pending | approved | rejected\n- `verifiedBy`, `verifiedAt`\n- `createdAt`","x":700,"y":-180,"width":400,"height":455},
		{"id":"therapist-alert","type":"text","text":"### 👨‍⚕️ Therapist Alert\n**WebSocket full-screen overlay**\n\n- AI confidence + reason\n- Location: city, district\n- Auto-escalate countdown *(5s)*\n\n**Actions:**\n- ✅ CONFIRM → escalate now\n- ❌ CANCEL → false alarm\n- ⏱️ No response → auto-escalate\n\n*Therapist can cancel until voice agent completes opening statement*","x":1220,"y":830,"width":360,"height":410},
		{"id":"timing-note","type":"text","text":"**⏱️ 10-Second Guarantee**\n\n| Step | Budget |\n|---|---|\n| Spike → upload | ~1s |\n| Claude triage | ~2s |\n| Therapist alert | ~0.5s |\n| Response window | **5s** |\n| Auto-escalate dial | ~1.5s |\n| **Total (auto-path)** | **~10s** |","x":1230,"y":-650,"width":320,"height":310},
		{"id":"crisis-header","type":"text","text":"## 🚨 Crisis Safety System (10s Pipeline)","x":1680,"y":-1040,"width":420,"height":100},
		{"id":"crisis-detection","type":"text","text":"### 🔊 Layer 1: Client Detection\n**Browser-side capture**\n\n- Web Audio AnalyserNode\n- `SPIKE_THRESHOLD`: 160/255\n- Sustained >1.5s triggers capture\n- 30s audio ring buffer *(MediaRecorder)*\n- 64×64 JPEG snapshot every 3s\n- Front camera always active *(consented)*\n- Mute = detection paused + warning","x":1700,"y":-810,"width":400,"height":320},
		{"id":"ai-triage","type":"text","text":"### 🤖 Layer 2: AI Triage\n**Claude API classifier**\n\n**Input:**\n- image: base64 JPEG *(64×64)*\n- audio_transcript: Whisper tiny\n- session_meta: ID, timestamp, therapist\n\n**Output:**\n- `CRISIS` → trigger Layer 3\n- `FALSE_ALARM` → log & discard\n\n**Audit:** session_id, result, reason, timestamp *(permanent)*","x":1660,"y":-350,"width":400,"height":430},
		{"id":"schedules","type":"text","text":"### 🗓️ schedules\n**Recurring availability**\n\n- `id`: serial **(PK)**\n- `doctorId`: text → **users.id (FK)**\n- `dayOfWeek`: int *(0-6)*\n- `startTime` / `endTime`: text *(\"HH:MM\")*\n- `slotDuration`: int *(30)*\n- `isRecurring`: boolean\n- `specificDate`: date\n- `createdAt`","x":1210,"y":-240,"width":360,"height":350},
		{"id":"redis-storage","type":"text","text":"### 💾 KV Temp Storage\n**24h TTL crisis cache**\n\n`Key:` crisis:{session_id}:{timestamp}\n`TTL:` 24h *(72h if escalation active)*\n`Encryption:` AES-256-GCM\n\n**Fields:**\n- location_lat / location_lng\n- snapshot_ref *(S3 key)*\n- audio_ref *(S3 key)*\n- triage_result / triage_reason\n- escalation_status\n- consent_record_id\n\n**Policy:** Auto-delete. Never sold.","x":2560,"y":-350,"width":340,"height":460},
		{"id":"voice-agent","type":"text","text":"### 📞 AI Voice Agent\n**Twilio + ElevenLabs TTS**\n\n**Languages:** English + Sinhala\n\n**Script:**\n\"Automated safety alert from ZenDoc. Patient last known location: [district], [city]. Therapist confirmed emergency. Releasing coordinates and session reference now.\"\n\n**Released:** GPS coords, city/district, session ref, timestamp, therapist callback\n\n**NOT released:** Patient name, account, AV data, biometrics","x":2100,"y":110,"width":360,"height":420}
	],
